<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="glow-n">glow <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɡləʊ/    美 /ɡloʊ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1n">1.<strong>n [常用单数] 稳定柔和的光；红晕；激情：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the warm <strong>glow of</strong> the setting sun
落日柔和的余晖</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a glow of pleasure</strong> / <strong>satisfaction</strong> / <strong>pride</strong>
强烈的愉悦感/满足感/自豪感</p></div></div>